To restart at the beginning of the day

% cd wccli

% lsvirtualenv	            # lists the virtual environments

% workon wccli            # ps workon is at the end of ~/.zshrc & points to to wcgui in ~/Envs  

% cd src/data

% python3 wordcounter.py gettysburg.txt 
 
% pip3 freeze >requirements.txt






